reviewText:
I rated this a 4 star,  as it is a very good video,  tastefully done with good instructions, but the quality of the video seemed to be over espoused (perhaps a copy of a copy?)

 I would not let this stop you from purchasing this video however.
Once you get past the narrator, the plot and the massage moves are good.  This is a help for couples who need to rediscover intimacy.

Demonstrated sensual massage in an intimate environment.  The intro and cut scenes with the couple watching the video are a bit distracting; I think that they could have spent more time demonstrating different techniques.

I bought several of the DVDs in this series and am quite pleased with all of them.  If you don't regularly share massage with your mate you don't know what you're missing... a well-done full body massage will relax you like nothing else.  This DVD provides great step-by-step instructions and covers everything from head-to-toe, including a luxurious rubdown with aromatic oils. Check it out and surprise your man with your new skills :)  And guys, believe me, there is nothing like a good massage to get your woman going.
